                            "Subject": "create your task list for tommorrow",
                            "Body": "<p class=\"editor-paragraph\">Hi,<br><br>A little nudge for your day 🤍<br><br>If you’re in the mood to plan things out (today or tomorrow),<br>your planner is waiting for you here:<br>👉 <a href=\"https://projectwebdemo-evdaf5etagb7fkeh.centralindia-01.azurewebsites.net/planner.html\" class=\"editor-link\">Planner</a><br><br>You can quickly add tasks, repeat your routines, and set up your day the way you like.<br><br>And if you’ve already planned and just want to check off what you’ve completed,<br>your dashboard is right here:<br>👉 <a href=\"https://projectwebdemo-evdaf5etagb7fkeh.centralindia-01.azurewebsites.net/\" class=\"editor-link\">DayDraft Checklist</a><br><br>Watch your progress build up as you go — one small task at a time ✨<br><br>Take it slow, stay consistent, and make your day yours 🌸<br><br>— DayDraft</p><br><p class=\"editor-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://projectwebdemo-evdaf5etagb7fkeh.centralindia-01.azurewebsites.net\" class=\"editor-link\">your task Dashboard</a></p>"
